      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（俺はコンビニで栄養ドリンクを買い込むと）\n（そのうちの一本を飲み干した）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I walk to a convenience store and buy an energy drink）\n（gulping it all down in one go.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さくら？　こんな時間に買い物？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura? Isn’t it late to be out shopping?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.410476203759512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。ちょうど歯磨き粉がなくなっちゃって\nそれでみんなとジャンケンで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ we just ran out of toothpaste.\nWe did Rock‚ Paper‚ Scissors for it and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4199773113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "負けた訳か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You lost.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.18664397795995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。{user}さんは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep. What about you‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.89800455172857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、夜食をちょっとね……\nまだ少し仕事残ってるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ just grabbing a late night snack.\nI’ve still got some work to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.863555816809328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "大変ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.126914191246023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、大変っちゃ大変か\nでも、全然、そんなこと思ったことないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I guess you could say that.\nBut I’ve never seen it that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.96430653731027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "いいですよね、そういうの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That must be nice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.76430653731027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、私は病気で、夢中になりたくても\nなかなかなれなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ I didn’t really have a chance\nto get passionate about anything because of my sickness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.66292333602908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはどうして\n今の仕事しようと思ったんです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why did you decide to work\nas a manager‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4121750196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "誘われたんだよ\n高校の時……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someone asked me.\nWhen I was in high school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5337979862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "高校？\nその時から、マネージャーなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "High school?\nYou started out that young?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.0504645574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "アルバイトだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it was a part-time job back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.81713122413275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "誘ったのは三枝さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did Saegusa-san ask you to join?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.602187934375976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈に誘われたとは言いづらいな）\n（妹の琴乃にも言っていないのに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I’m not sure I can tell her Mana asked me.）\n（I haven’t even told Kotono about that.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.40529448872523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "……じゃあ\nどうして私を合格にしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well…\n…why you let me pass the audition?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7386278221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 72.30529448872522
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 72.30529448872522
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "――俺に、預からせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――I’ll take her on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.30529448872522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_way-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 76.8555330345
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_street-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 77.0719611553919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "あの話をすると、みんな信じられないって……\nもしかしたら一目惚れでもしたんじゃないかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I told everyone‚ they couldn’t believe it.\nThey thought you might’ve fallen in love with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.5386278221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ははは……そんなことはないよ。アイドルとしては\n一目惚れしたと言えるかもしれないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahah… No‚ it wasn’t that. But you could say\nI fell in love with the idol I saw in you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.20985232080736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "そんなにアイドルに向いてると思ったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really thought I had that much potential?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.70985232080736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "いや、単なる勘かもしれないけど、見た時思ったんだ\nこれは逃しちゃいけないって……なんとなく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ call it a hunch‚ but when I saw you‚\nI thought to myself‚ “Don’t miss this opportunity.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……じゃあ、私と一緒だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… That makes two of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.23529455548244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "私も{user}さんを見た時に\n心臓がドキンといったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I saw you‚\nmy heart skipped a beat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.16132636751456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "あ、この人だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought to myself‚ “He’s the one.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.99894544964752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "あ、変な意味じゃないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not in a weird way or anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、ずっと探してたものが見つかったって……\nここでいいんだって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It just felt like I’d found what I was looking for all this time.\nAnd it was here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3980384736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_05_05-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらはそう言うと胸に手を当てた）\n（心臓がそう言ってた、と伝えたいのだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Saying this‚ Sakura places her hand on her chest.）\n（As if to say it was her heart who had told her.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.38260010764733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 137.88260010764742
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dormitory-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 137.88260010764742
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
